commit_message:
Let the fpga programming api call cyborg agent

Also added glance client to download images

Use following curl to trigger the api

curl -s -X PATCH -H "X-Auth-Token: $OS_TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json"\
  -d '[{
    	"path": "/program",
    	"op": "replace",
    	"value": [{
    		"image_uuid": "{image_uuid}"
    	}]
  }]'\
  http://{HOST_IP}:6666/v1/accelerators/deployables/{deployable_uuid}/program

